template.description:
To use template create new user 'api' and set user type 'Zabbix Super Admin'.

Setup global macros:
{$Z_API_USER}
{$Z_API_PASSWORD}
{$Z_API_PHP}
{$Z_API_SESSIONID}

for example:

{$Z_API_USER} = 'api'
{$Z_API_PASSWORD} = 'jp5Jda5ABveGVEbSyJgZ'
{$Z_API_PHP} = 'http://127.0.0.1/api_jsonrpc.php'

Obtain new session id instantly
curl -sk http://127.0.0.1/api_jsonrpc.php -X POST -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -H 'cache-control: no-cache' -d '{"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"user.login","params":{"user":"api","password":"jp5Jda5ABveGVEbSyJgZ"},"id":1}' | grep -E -o "([0-9a-f]{32,32})"

Install session:
{$Z_API_SESSIONID} = '2fdcdb96409fb134f82a2029342ce933'
